        <updateDate>2006-11-28T17:35:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[Safer Roads Everywhere Act - Amends Federal highway law to authorize the Secretary of Transportation, in exercising his or her authority to increase highway safety, to improve through specified traffic safety-related activities worldwide traffic safety and reduce the burden of deaths and injuries from traffic accidents.]]></text>
